room_title: Escape room "The Temple" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: What a great room! Very creative games and cool use of tech. It looks amazing too. You can tell these guys put a lot of effort into their rooms, it's not just another plain room with boxes in it. Highly recommended for any escape room enthusiast!

room_title: Escape room "The Temple" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: The room looked incredible and was a ton of fun! And there were no traditional locks or boxes in the room at all! Awesome experience.
